import React, { Fragment } from 'react'
import Grid from '@material-ui/core/Grid'
import Card from './Card'
import PlayerStats from "./PlayerStats"
import TextField from '@material-ui/core/TextField'


const styles = {
    card: {
      padding: 20,
    }
  };


export default props =>
    <Fragment>
        <Grid container justify="center">
            <TextField
              id="standard-name"
              label="Player 1"
              margin="normal"
            />
            <TextField
              id="standard-name"
              label="Player 2"
              margin="normal"
            />
        </Grid>
        
        <Grid container justify="center">
            <Card style={styles.card} key={0} name="Muma" team="Houston Outlaws" link="https://bnetcmsus-a.akamaihd.net/cms/page_media/EZTH4390SJCR1526600596230.png"/>
            <Card key={1} name="sinatraa" team="San Francisco Shock" link="https://bnetcmsus-a.akamaihd.net/cms/page_media/GAH625QTQPGC1512777247784.png"/>
        </Grid>
        <Grid container justify="center">
            <PlayerStats />
            <PlayerStats />
        </Grid>
    </Fragment>
